  "description": "德國哲學家（1889－1976）",
  "bio": "馬丁·海德格（德語：Martin Heidegger，1889年9月26日—1976年5月26日），德國哲學家，海德格對於存在、時間、技術、語言和真理等問題有著獨特的見解。代表作有《存在與時間》、《形上學導論》等。在現象學、存在主義、解構主義、詮釋學、後現代主義、政治理論、心理學及神學有舉足輕重的影響。",
  "bio_source": "zhwiki",
  "description_en": "German philosopher (1889–1976)",
  "bio_en": "Martin Heidegger (26 September 1889 – 26 May 1976) was a German philosopher whose work was central to the development of phenomenology, hermeneutics, and existentialism. He has had significant impact within subsequent philosophy, social sciences and humanities, and theology.\nHeidegger's magnum opus, Being and Time (1927), is widely considered one of the most significant works of modern philosophy.",
  "bio_en_source": "enwiki"
}